Changes
=======

Unless otherwise noted, all changes by Daisuke Maki

0.05 - 28 May 2007
  - Migrate to Module::Install
  - Require new version for modules.
  - Add POD tests.

0.04 - 29 Jun 2005
  - No code change
  - Change Makefile.PL target to 'traditional'
  - minor doc tweaks

0.03 - 24 Jul 2004
  - Handle infinite datetimes

0.02 - 22 Jan 2004
  - Do calculations based on Asia/Shanghai time zone
  - Slightly beef up tests

0.01 - 12 Jan 2004
  - Remove reference to non-existent DateTime::Event::SolarTerm::Data
  - Add Makefile.PL for backwards compatibility

0.01_01 - 27 Dec 2003
  - Initial release
